'''Piggs Peak Airfield''' {{airport codes||FDNG}} is an airport serving [[Piggs Peak]] in the [[Hhohho Region]] of [[Swaziland]]. The airport is at [[Ngonini]], an agricultural village {{convert|24|km}} northeast of Piggs Peak.
'''Caution:''' There is a power line that runs along the east side of the runway, and crosses the approach/departure path at the south end. The crossing cables are unmarked.
